"tid":1100426,"uid":30215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T12:22:55.000Z","msg":"英國佬又埋地雷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a914bf24fb17713bb40127b8d0bed43df9cf4e25","tid":1100426,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"釋法啦 Diu"},{"pid":"74896d003a95d4016f1dc479e200cc2bb1704096","tid":1100426,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T12:55:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過，執行官員卻沒有執行這項指令，令新界原居民男丁皆可申請建丁屋。1980年民政署內部報告指出，該署發現寫漏了該項條款，並指出丁屋政策實施數年，已出現嚴重濫用問題，建議政府盡快為丁屋政策「補漏」，否則勢必禍延至1997年。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英國對「禍延至1997年」應該係樂見其成<br />\n你支那國威迫搶我領土, 我為乜要CARE你97年後點撚樣？<br />\n<br />\n單程證家庭團聚都係, 係90年代已開始"},{"pid":"6393eff533b45ba57b30a56fb92bad20484f0208","tid":1100426,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:59:58.000Z","msg":"豬隊友"},{"pid":"834424f5b66dadd5b486a3c3fdfed2ae1992cb1c","tid":1100426,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"有幾難冇屋住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00939d71f118bdd5a38a0549e077921a2aad11a","tid":1100426,"uid":238454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:07:08.000Z","msg":"同政府講：我無屋住，就可以起啦"},{"pid":"4efd88aa53795e5b2e24ed4b6ec5abf24c7cc88e","tid":1100426,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:08:52.000Z","msg":"英國佬 搞搞震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8a67f400a58399897d55624ef10d86bb7d7ac7","tid":1100426,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1c906f0638bff59bcc5ae56cb23089e4e08266","tid":1100426,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:50:06.000Z","msg":"要無屋住有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同首次置業咁一樣有漏洞可鑽"},"citedBy":0,"rep